{"tid":2010312,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"防暴與傳媒聯絡隊內閧？有警員要同袍「掃背脊」安撫情緒","createTime":"2020-05-10T10:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T19:14:18.000Z","uid":1886,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"ac87dd48965844ddb7b18f7ce025ac9e99d72cf4","tid":2010312,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T10:32:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10158985338777448/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10158985338777448%2F&d=18ndJK2uCT0lbSM6MbdNQjbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=194f98ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10158985338777448/</a><br />\n<br />\n警方聲稱接報有人於尖沙嘴海港城內聚眾，海量警員突然於下午4時許闖入商場內趕人及拉起封鎖線，其間記者堆一直被警員逼退，縮至一隅的梯間位置。<br />\n<br />\n有防暴警打算上前進一步逼退記者，但被當時在場開咪指揮的傳媒聯絡隊高振邦一手推開。<br />\n<br />\n傳媒聯絡隊要求記者退後，但有防暴警疑不耐煩，一直「指手劃腳」，似乎想朝記者堆強行推進。但高振邦再次阻止，疑似講出「喂指揮官，邊個揸莊呢度？」，然後兩隊人內閧，其中一名防暴警情緒比較激動，要由其他警員拉走，以及拍膊頭、掃背脊安撫。不過該名警員則繼續在一旁與同袍盡訴不滿。 <br />\n<br />\n【尖沙嘴海港城市民眾集 防暴警衝入商場一度與同袍爆口角】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/35JEJ5e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F35JEJ5e&d=18ndJK2uCT0lbSM6MbdNQjbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=92aec6d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/35JEJ5e</a><br />\n<br />\n【多區和你Sing 防暴警太古城票控4人 荃灣警告有線記者涉犯限聚令】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3cltnXF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cltnXF&d=18ndJK2uCT0lbSM6MbdNQjbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=0708c951\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3cltnXF</a>"},{"pid":"982c01161c6eead13ff9e7499479cbe477aca60c","tid":2010312,"uid":280848,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T10:34:50.000Z","msg":"細路仔扭計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde6079d92e3e6e3d41a9df99a60f0bc8348b610","tid":2010312,"uid":124623,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T10:36:56.000Z","msg":"懷疑果個防暴有份偷上次d毒品，上晒電咁<img src=\"/assets/